{"id": "pos039", "name": "Cam_Noah_702_09_09", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "Door Opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "... Why are you still awake?\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena?\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "... Yeah. Sorry, I was thinking about something.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "You... Why did you start smoking again?\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "... Smoke outside. You don't want Aroma to smell the cigarette smoke.\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "... (Exhales)... She isn't willing to accept any work these days. I'm trying to figure out a way to handle that.\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Noah... I...\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "......?\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "I don't think I... can bear it anymore...\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "......\nYou should ask someone else in the company to take over your job. You're burning the candle at both ends.\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "No, it's not about my job.\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "......?\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "After the 7th anniversary concert, her speech and actions have become stranger and stranger... She sings melodies she's never heard of and reminisces about foreign sceneries. She even constantly asks me questions that never belong to her memory in the first place... You know what I'm saying, right?\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena, you...\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "The memories that originally exist in that body...\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Shhh! <font size=\"1.6\">That's enough talk on this topic.</font>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Why... Stop deceiving yourself! Noah! Your experiment was not successful at all!\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "... What are you talking about? Aren't you the one who insisted that I stop back then? We had it! We had a really good shot at bringing back Aroma for real! The fact that we stopped at that half-a**ed state is why...\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Then did you want me to just watch as you continued on with that ridiculous experiment!? You know very well yourself that bringing Aroma back was asking the impossible! It's all because of you that we're in this hole now...\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Because of me!? If not for me, your younger sister would already be dead!\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">THAT'S NOT MY SISTER!!</font>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "image", "attrs": ["pos3901"], "content": ""}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Ummm...!\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">Keep your voice down! She'll hear us!</font>\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "......!\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "I... For the past few years, I've continued to conduct this research for her sake. I also collected a lot of new data from her stabilizers. I still haven't given up on the possibility of resetting her memory and turning her into the real Aroma.\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "... But if we do that...\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "That's right. There's a possibility that her memory of these past seven years she spent with us will disappear as well. This is a risk we cannot avoid, and it's also why I couldn't make up my mind. \nIn these seven years, although things were tough for her, it certainly has given her some very happy memories too.\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Regardless, there is no turning back for us. From now on, no matter what decision we make, we can only face it together... However, one thing remains unchanged. We must let her live on. Not knowing anything, and not needing to shoulder anything. Just live on happily. Don't you agree?\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "... I don't know anymore... To save her, we erased a living person from existence, and at this very moment, that person clearly still exists within her body.\nSometimes, when I look into her eyes... I see that \"other\" girl. This guilt... I have no idea what can even be considered happiness to \"them\" anymore.\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena, we need to focus on \"Aroma\". She's the most important one. I believe that we'll have to make a decision in the very near future...\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "... We have one more option.\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "......?\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Tell her.\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Eh?\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Tell her. Tell her everything. Let her decide what she'll do herself... even if she despises us because of it. I know this sounds a bit irresponsible, but I believe that this is the correct thing to do.\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "... I'll... consider it...\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "ドアを開ける"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "まだ寝てなかったのかい？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……ごめんなさい。考えごとをしていて。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena……またタバコを吸い始めたのか？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……外で吸おう。\nAromaちゃんにタバコの煙を吸わせないように。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……ふぅ……あの子、最近仕事を受けようとしないの。\nどうしようか考えてるところ。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Noah……私……\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "もう……無理かもって……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "………\n会社の他の人に仕事を変わってもらった方がいい。\nこのままじゃ、君が壊れちゃう。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "違う……仕事のことじゃないの。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "7周年のライブから……あの子の様子がおかしいの……\n聞いたこともない曲を口ずさんだり、知らない景色を懐かしいと言ったり……\nそれに、あの子のものじゃない記憶について私に聞いてくる……\n私の言ってる意味が、分かるでしょう？\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena，君……\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "元の身体の持ち主の記憶……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "しーっ！<font size=\"1.6\">その話はもうやめよう。</font>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "なんで……もう自分をだますのはやめましょう！\nNoah！あなたの実験は成功しなかったのよ！\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……何を言ってるんだ？\nあの時やめようと言ってきかなかったのは君だろう？\n僕は、本当にAromaちゃんを取り戻すことができると、信じていたのに！\nあんな中途半端なことろで……だから……\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "私にあんな光景をただ見てろっていうの！？\nあなただって分かってるはずよ。\nAromaを取り戻すなんて、最初から不可能だったのよ！\nこんなことになったのも全部……全部あなたのせい……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "僕のせいだって！？\n僕がいなければ、君の妹はとっくに死んでいた！\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">あんなの私の妹じゃない！</font>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "image", "attrs": ["pos3901"], "content": ""}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "うぅ……っ！\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">声が大きい！聞こえるだろう！</font>\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "僕は……Aromaちゃんのために研究を続けてきた。\nあの子の安定器から取れたデータも少なくない。\n僕はあの子の記憶を諦めたたことなんかない。\nあの子が本物のAromaちゃんになる希望を捨てたことなんかないんだ。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……でもそんなことをしたら……\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "そうだよ。\nこの7年の記憶は消えてしまうかもしれない。\nこれは、僕たちが受け入れないといけないリスクだ。\nそして、僕がずっと迷ってるのもこれが原因だ。\nこの7年、確かに大変だったけど、でもあの子にとって完全に楽しい記憶がないわけじゃない。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "とにかく、僕たちはもう後戻りはできないんだ。\nこれからどんな選択をしようと、僕たちは一緒に向き合わなきゃいけない……\nでも一つだけ変わらないことがある。\nそれは、あの子に生きてもらうこと。\n何も知らずに、何も背負わずに、幸せに生きてもらうことだ。\nそうだろう？\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……私にはもう分らないわ……\nあの子を救うために、他人を殺した。\nそれに、私たちが殺したあの女の子は、確実にAromaの身体の中にいる。\nあの子の目を見ていると……分からなくなるのよ……\n「あの子たち」にとって何が幸せなのか。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena、僕たちは「Aromaちゃん」のために考えるべきだ。\n一番大事なのはあの子なんだから。\nおそらく、選択の時はもう近い……\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……あと一つ選択肢があるわ。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "あの子に話すの。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "え？\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "全てを。\n全てをあの子に話すのよ。\nそして、あの子自身に決めさせるの……\nこれで、あの子が私たちを恨むことになったとしてもね。\n無責任に聞こえる？\nでも、私はこれが一番正しい選択だと思うわ。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……考えてみるよ……\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……妳怎麼還沒睡？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……嗯，抱歉，我在想事情。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "妳……怎麼又開始抽煙了？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……去外面抽吧，別讓 Aroma 聞到煙味。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……呼……她完全不願意接最近的工作，我正在想辦法處理。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Noah……我……\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "我好像已經……快撐不下去了……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……。\n讓公司其他的人來接妳的工作吧，妳這樣太操勞了。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "不，不是工作的問題。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "自從七週年演唱會後，她的言行就越來越奇怪……唱著沒聽過的旋律，懷念著陌生的景象，甚至一直問我一些根本不屬於她記憶中的問題……你懂我的意思吧？\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena，妳……\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "原本存在那副身體的記憶……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "噓！<font size=\"1.6\">這個話題別再繼續了。</font>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "為什麼……別再騙自己了！Noah！你的實驗根本沒有成功！\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……妳在說什麼？當初堅持終止的是妳吧？我們本來很有希望可以真的把 Aroma 帶回來的！就是因為停在那種半吊子的地方，才會……\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "難道要我眼睜睜看你繼續那種荒唐的事嗎！？你自己也很清楚，把 Aroma 帶回來什麼的根本不可能！會變成這樣都是因為你……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "因為我！？要不是我，你妹妹早就死了！\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">那根本不是我妹妹！！</font>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "image", "attrs": ["pos3901"], "content": ""}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "捂……！\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">小聲點！她會聽見的！</font>\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "我……這些年都還持續為了她在進行這項研究，也從她的穩壓器上蒐集到不少新的數據。我仍然沒有放棄重置她的記憶，讓她變成真正的 Aroma 的可能。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……但是那麼做……\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "沒錯，這七年來她與我們相處的記憶也有機會會消失，這是我們得承擔的風險，也是我為什麼一直猶豫不決的原因。這七年中，雖然很辛苦，但對她來說也不是完全沒有快樂的回憶。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "無論如何，我們已經無法回頭了，現在做什麼選擇，都只能由我們一起面對……但不變的是，我們必須讓她活下去，什麼都不知道，也什麼都不必承擔，幸福地活下去，不是嗎？\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……我已經不知道了……我們為了救她，抹殺掉了一個人，而現在那個人確實還殘存在她身體裡，偶爾看著她的眼睛……我就會看見她，這種罪惡感……我已經不知道對「她們」來說到底怎樣才是幸福了。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena，我們必須專心在「Aroma」身上，她才是最重要的。我想我們很快必須做出選擇……\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……我們還有一個選項。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "告訴她吧。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "咦？\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "把一切都告訴她，讓她自己決定該怎麼做……即使她會因此而痛恨我們。這聽上去有些不負責任，不過我認為這才是正確的。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……我……會考慮看看的……\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "문이 열린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "...안 자고 뭐 해?\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena?\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "...응. 미안. 뭐 좀 생각하고 있었어.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "너... 담배 끊지 않았어?\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "...바깥에서 펴. Aroma가 담배연기 맡을 수도 있으니까.\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "...후... 요즘 저 아이... 일을 하고 싶지 않아 해... 어떻게 처리를 해야 할지 생각하고 있었어.\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Noah... 나...\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": ".......?\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "더 이상은... 못할 것 같아...\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "......\n회사의 다른 사람에게 네 일을 맡겨도 되잖아. 이대로면 네 몸도 금방 망가져버릴 거야.\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "아니... 일 얘기를 하는 게 아니야.\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "......?\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "7주년 콘서트 이후로, 저 아이의 말이 조금씩 이상해지고 있어... 한 번도 들어본 적이 없는 멜로디를 부른다거나, 낯선 기억들을 그리워한다거나... 게다가... 자신의 기억이 아닌 일들까지 내게 물어보곤 해... 무슨 뜻인지 알 것 같아?\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena, 너...\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "원래 그 몸에 들어 있었던 기억...\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "쉿! <font size=\"1.6\">그 얘긴 여기서 할 얘기가 아니야!</font>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "뭐야... 이제 자신까지 속이는 짓은 그만둬! Noah! 당신 실험은 성공한 게 아니었어!\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "...무슨 말을 하는 거야? 그때 고집을 부리며 막아섰던 건 너잖아? 우리는 확실히 Aroma를 되돌릴 수 있을 기회가 있었어! 뭔가 애매한 상태에서 그런 결정을 내렸기 때문에....\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "내가 그런 터무니없는 짓을 하는 당신의 모습을 계속 볼 거라고 생각해!? 당신도 알고 있잖아. Aroma를 되살린다는 건 애초에 불가능하다는 것을! 이렇게 된 것도 전부 당신 때문에...\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "나 때문이라고!?\n내가 아니었으면, 네 동생은 진작에 죽었어!\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">그 아인 내 동생이 아니야!!</font>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "image", "attrs": ["pos3901"], "content": ""}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "크흑...!\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">목소리를 낮춰! 들리겠어!</font>\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "......!\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "난... 이 몇 년 간 그 아이를 위해서 이 연구를 진행했어. 그 아이의 안정 장치로부터 수많은 데이터를 모으기도 했고. 난 그 아이의 기억을 리셋하고 다시 이식하는 일을... 저 아이가 진짜 Aroma로 다시 태어날 가능성을 한시도 포기한 적이 없어.\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "...하지만 그렇게 하면...\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "맞아. 이 7년 동안 저 아이가 우리와 함께 했던 기억이 사라져버릴지도 모르지. 이건 우리가 감수해야 할 부분이기도 했고 내가 망설인 이유 역시 이것 때문이었어. 7년 동안 그렇게 고생했지만, 그래도 저 아이에게 나쁜 기억만 남겨준 것도 아니잖아.\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "어쨌든 우린 이미 돌이킬 수 없어. 지금 어떤 선택을 하든, 우리는 그 선택을  감수해야만 해. 하지만 변하지 않는 것은... 우리는 무조건 저 아이가 살아갈 수 있도록 해야 해. 아무것도 모른 채로, 아무것도 짊어지지 않고 행복하게 살아갈 수 있도록...\n내 말이 틀려?\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "...이젠 나도 모르겠어... 그 아이를 구하기 위해 우리는... 한 사람을 죽였어. 그리고 그 사람도 지금 저 육체에 확실히 존재하고 있어. 가끔 그 아이의 눈을 바라보고 있으면... 그 사람을 만나게 돼. 그때 드는 죄책감은 정말이지... 이것이 진정 「저들」에게 행복한 일일까? 난 정말 모르겠어.\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena, 우리는 「Aroma」만을 생각하면 돼. 가장 중요한 건 그 아이야. 우리는 빨리 결정을 내려야만 해...\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "...한 가지 선택이 더 있어.\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "......?\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "저 아이에게 털어놓자.\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "뭐?\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "전부 저 아이에게 말해줘서, 저 아이가 스스로 무엇을 해야 할지 결정하도록 해주자고... 설령 우리를 증오하게 된다 하더라도. 무책임하게 들리더라도 그게 맞는 것 같아.\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "...그건... 나도 다시 신중하게 생각해볼게...\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……妳怎麼還沒睡？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……嗯，抱歉，我在想事情。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "妳……怎麼又開始抽煙了？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……去外面抽吧，別讓 Aroma 聞到煙味。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……呼……她完全不願意接最近的工作，我正在想辦法處理。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Noah……我……\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "我好像已經……快撐不下去了……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……。\n讓公司其他的人來接妳的工作吧，妳這樣太操勞了。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "不，不是工作的問題。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "自從七週年演唱會後，她的言行就越來越奇怪……唱著沒聽過的旋律，懷念著陌生的景象，甚至一直問我一些根本不屬於她記憶中的問題……你懂我的意思吧？\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena，妳……\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "原本存在那副身體的記憶……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "噓！<font size=\"1.6\">這個話題別再繼續了。</font>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "為什麼……別再騙自己了！Noah！你的實驗根本沒有成功！\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……妳在說什麼？當初堅持終止的是妳吧？我們本來很有希望可以真的把 Aroma 帶回來的！就是因為停在那種半吊子的地方，才會……\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "難道要我眼睜睜看你繼續那種荒唐的事嗎！？你自己也很清楚，把 Aroma 帶回來什麼的根本不可能！會變成這樣都是因為你……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "因為我！？要不是我，你妹妹早就死了！\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">那根本不是我妹妹！！</font>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "image", "attrs": ["pos3901"], "content": ""}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "捂……！\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">小聲點！她會聽見的！</font>\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "我……這些年都還持續為了她在進行這項研究，也從她的穩壓器上蒐集到不少新的數據。我仍然沒有放棄重置她的記憶，讓她變成真正的 Aroma 的可能。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……但是那麼做……\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "沒錯，這七年來她與我們相處的記憶也有機會會消失，這是我們得承擔的風險，也是我為什麼一直猶豫不決的原因。這七年中，雖然很辛苦，但對她來說也不是完全沒有快樂的回憶。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "無論如何，我們已經無法回頭了，現在做什麼選擇，都只能由我們一起面對……但不變的是，我們必須讓她活下去，什麼都不知道，也什麼都不必承擔，幸福地活下去，不是嗎？\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……我已經不知道了……我們為了救她，抹殺掉了一個人，而現在那個人確實還殘存在她身體裡，偶爾看著她的眼睛……我就會看見她，這種罪惡感……我已經不知道對「她們」來說到底怎樣才是幸福了。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena，我們必須專心在「Aroma」身上，她才是最重要的。我想我們很快必須做出選擇……\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……我們還有一個選項。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "告訴她吧。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "咦？\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "把一切都告訴她，讓她自己決定該怎麼做……即使她會因此而痛恨我們。這聽上去有些不負責任，不過我認為這才是正確的。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……我……會考慮看看的……\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "开门"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……妳怎么还没睡？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……嗯，抱歉，我在想事情。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "妳……怎么又开始抽烟了？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……去外面抽吧，别让 Aroma 闻到烟味。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……呼……她完全不愿意接最近的工作，我正在想办法处理。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Noah……我……\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "我好像已经……快撑不下去了……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……。\n让公司其他的人来接妳的工作吧，妳这样太操劳了。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "不，不是工作的问题。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "自从七周年演唱会后，她的言行就越来越奇怪……唱着没听过的旋律，怀念着陌生的景象，甚至一直问我一些根本不属于她记忆中的问题……你懂我的意思吧？\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena，妳……\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "原本存在那副身体的记忆……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "嘘！ <font size=\"1.6\">这个话题别再继续了。 </font>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "为什么……别再骗自己了！ Noah！你的实验根本没有成功！\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……妳在说什么？当初坚持终止的是妳吧？我们本来很有希望可以真的把 Aroma 带回来的！就是因为停在那种半吊子的地方，才会……\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "难道要我眼睁睁看你继续那种荒唐的事吗！ ？你自己也很清楚，把 Aroma 带回来什么的根本不可能！会变成这样都是因为你……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "因为我！ ？要不是我，你妹妹早就死了！\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">那根本不是我妹妹！ ！ </font>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "image", "attrs": ["pos3901"], "content": ""}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "捂……！\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">小声点！她会听见的！ </font>\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "我……这些年都还持续为了她在进行这项研究，也从她的稳压器上搜集到不少新的数据。我仍然没有放弃重置她的记忆，让她变成真正的 Aroma 的可能。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……但是那么做……\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "没错，这七年来她与我们相处的记忆也有机会会消失，这是我们得承担的风险，也是我为什么一直犹豫不决的原因。这七年中，虽然很辛苦，但对她来说也不是完全没有快乐的回忆。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "无论如何，我们已经无法回头了，现在做什么选择，都只能由我们一起面对……但不变的是，我们必须让她活下去，什么都不知道，也什么都不必承担，幸福地活下去，不是吗？\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……我已经不知道了……我们为了救她，抹杀掉了一个人，而现在那个人确实还残存在她身体里，偶尔看着她的眼睛……我就会看见她，这种罪恶感… …我已经不知道对「她们」来说到底怎样才是幸福了。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena，我们必须专心在「Aroma」身上，她才是最重要的。我想我们很快必须做出选择……\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……我们还有一个选项。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "告诉她吧。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "咦？\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "把一切都告诉她，让她自己决定该怎么做……即使她会因此而痛恨我们。这听上去有些不负责任，不过我认为这才是正确的。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……我……会考虑看看的……\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[讯号中断]</i>\n"}]]}